The '''[[Merr-Sonn Munitions, Inc./Legends|Merr-Sonn]] mobile grenade mortar''' was an assault vehicle used by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. It was capable of firing a total of approximately one hundred [[Grenade/Legends|grenades]] per second, with storage for hundreds more grenades that could be reloaded through a tube. It was operated by two [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtroopers]] on a [[Repulsorlift/Legends|repulsorlift]] sled; the vehicle could accelerate fast and rise up in the air up to thirty meters.<ref name="The Last of the Jedi: Dark Warning" />

In [[19 BBY/Legends|19 BBY]], two former [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]], [[Ferus Olin]] and [[Garen Muln]], were attacked in the [[Crystal Cave/Legends|Crystal Caves]] by thirty [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtroopers]] and a Merr-Sonn mobile grenade mortar.<ref name="The Last of the Jedi: Dark Warning" />

